# Frontend Environment Configuration

# Optional: override API base URL if you are not using the dev proxy.
# For single-machine dev: leave empty (proxy handles routing)
# For VM deployment: point to backend server
# Example: VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://10.0.0.20:8011
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=

# Optional: override the Vite dev-server proxy target (see vite.config.js).
# For single-machine dev: use localhost or 127.0.0.1
# For VM deployment: point to backend server IP
# Example: VITE_DEV_PROXY_TARGET=http://10.0.0.20:8011
# VITE_DEV_PROXY_TARGET=http://127.0.0.1:8011
